Content:
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2063] added more files
 to the wix package, added more 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2067] ansi colors
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2073] date formatting
, and more to the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2085] wix package
, also more 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2086] ``char``
