jonathandturner added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2064] configurable prompts
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2065] ``str collect``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2070] fixed invocations
, added the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2072] ``char``
 command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2084] released 0.16.0
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2100] ``each --numbered``
orientnab added more 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2068] command docs
