[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2074] ``cal``
 improvements
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2082] ``random dice``
, and a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2087] histogram+dice example
